| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2873 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6b74f6b4-b430-5ee3-aaab-1bfe55b0b2d7"
